<p class=\\"bb_p\\">Franz throws steel ball at Cybertruck window right before launch. Guess we have some improvements to make before production haha. pic.twitter.com/eB0o4tlPoz — Elon Musk (@elonmusk) November 23, 2019</p><div class="source"><p class=\\"bb_p align_right\\"><a rel="nofollow noreferrer" href="https://www.unian.ua/m/science/10768355-mask-poyasniv-chomu-u-bronovanogo-pikapa-cybertruck-na-prezentaciji-rozbilosya-sklo-video.html" target="_blank">За матеріалами "unian"</a></p></div>',
